data.description: Discover the blend of comfort & charm in this ranch home. An inviting living room sets the stage for a welcoming ambiance. The modern eat-in kitchen boasts ample storage, including a pantry with convenient pull-out shelves. Flowing from the kitchen, a spacious deck beckons for outdoor dining & relaxation. The primary bedroom is a spacious retreat, strategically secluded from the main living space & it's own deck access. 3 bedrooms, each with ample closet space & a full bath complete the first floor. The finished basement offers a flexible opportunity with it's own entrance & versatile space for recreation/business & a dedicated room for an office/den. Completing this lower level is a full bath, laundry room & extra storage-adding unique functionality. Enhancing convenience, 2 garages—1 is heated, measuring 35x13—along with 4 extra parking spots offering abundant space for vehicle & storage needs. Outside, a spacious yard presents the perfect canvas for creating an oasis. Welcome Home!
